  </div>

  <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mt-4 pt-10 text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    As Europeans, we share a common goal: to build a dynamic, secure, and prosperous Union that preserves our values while elevating quality of life for all. By fostering smart collaboration and leveraging shared resources, we can create a Europe where abundance, progress, and the freedom to truly live go hand in hand.
  </p>
